comment: Lin (LAL) jumps and makes contact with the arm of Kidd-Gilchrist (CHA), causing him to lose the ball on the play to the basket.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court was overturned and the ball was awarded to Los Angeles.
Hill (LAL) sets the screen on Kidd-Gilchrist (CHA) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Johnson (LAL) commits a take foul on Williams (CHA).
As Lin (LAL) drives to the basket, Kidd-Gilchrist (CHA) makes contact with the body of Lin, affecting his layup attempt.
Clarkson (LAL) commits a take foul on Henderson (CHA).
Hill (LAL) switches his pivot foot before handing the ball off on the perimeter.
Johnson (LAL) commits a take foul on Williams (CHA).
Hill (LAL) makes incidental contact with Zeller (CHA) as he drives for his layup attempt.
Clarkson (LAL) commits a take foul on Williams (CHA).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the shot was taken before the clock expired was upheld.
